function Start()
	for i, idMonster in ipairs(tMonsters) do
		Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(idMonster)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMonster, true)
	end
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	for i, idMonster in pairs(tMonsters) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonster) and not Hydra.ActorHasQueuedActions(idMonster) then
			Hydra.QActorWait(idMonster, Hydra.GetRandomFloat())
			Hydra.QActorPower(idMonster, S_ANIM_CHEERING, idMonster, true)
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorFaceActor(idActorSpawned, idDecor, true)
	
	table.insert(tMonsters, idActorSpawned)
end
